{"tid":2158663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傾城","createTime":"2020-08-15T22:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T14:56:42.000Z","uid":15954,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7582a0479495da0593a49b0c837e6549d082b6fc","tid":2158663,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:26:43.000Z","msg":"完場就算 出局了 輸波這一晚也重要 <br />\n完全累了 三弟嘲笑 多給我一點(錢) 切勿缺少<br />\n緣份盡了 也不緊要 記緊這淒慘的深宵<br />\n球場內裡 燈光普照 然而共你 再沒破曉<br />\n紅眼睛 幽幽的看著這孤城 如同苦笑 擠出的高興<br />\n全隊為冠 花光狠勁 浮華陣勢 作輸波佈景<br />\n傳說中 癡心的眼淚會傾城 霓虹熄了 世界漸冷清<br />\n丁狗會射 哥狗會完 顯得這故事尾聲 更動聽"},{"pid":"daa08d2c55dccd84d87dd0aafed625aea7248240","tid":2158663,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da73becb2a15ffc0d39e7279f0950596fa0d60a","tid":2158663,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074509e2d293e651bf1411aff0528800dd99d9dc","tid":2158663,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T23:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22588b4e0301d0386be634228e86d39410bea312","tid":2158663,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b960ca389f4149731ccbb7b94239674b2b1da2","tid":2158663,"uid":34858,"like":0,"disli